        day.” </b>(Jn.6:39,40,44,54)
      <p><b>
        “Martha saith unto him, I know that he shall rise again in the resurrection at the last day.” </b> (Jn.11:24)
      </p>
    <p><b>
        “He that rejecteth me, and receiveth not my words, hath one that judgeth him: the word that I have spoken, the
