    </p>
    <p>
      This chapter is merely a continuation of Paul’s thought in the latter part of chapter 4.  Although we will
      discuss 1 st Thess.4 a little later, the reader should study it now in order to acquaint himself with the entire
      topic of discussion.  After such a review, it will become obvious that the “rapture” or Christ’s second coming is
