      loved ones who had died will not be left out of this marvelous event of the second coming of Jesus.  In fact, he
      tells them that those which “sleep in Jesus” will actually accompany the Lord upon his return.
      But now, he turns his attention to the ungodly, and again reiterates that “sudden destruction” will come upon
      them.  This destruction is the “wrath” that God will execute upon the ungodly.  Notice the contrast: destruction to
