    </p>
    <p>
      I never cease to be amazed how someone can read these verses, and yet, come away with the interpretation of two
      comings of Jesus that are separated by a period of seven years.  Of course, the dispensationalist attempts to
      make a distinction between the “rapture” and the “second coming”.  They maintain that the rapture or “parousia”
